/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><img class=\"detail-desc-decorate-image\" src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S071d0105069b48fbb82604043ea99198v.jpeg\" slate-data-type=\"image\"/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><img class=\"detail-desc-decorate-image\" src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sab98a22c610847d3b8e675228e7f1dbbu.jpg\" slate-data-type=\"image\"/></div><div class=\"detailmodule_image\"><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><img class=\"detail-desc-decorate-image\" src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sb4ce8aca96f94e6d835aaeb48ac3cdc8e.jpg\" slate-data-type=\"image\"/></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">FAQ</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">1) Q: When can I make the payment and how many hours can I send it?</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">A: Ship within 48 hours and provide track number.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">2) Q: How long will it take me to receive the package? If not, what should I do?</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">A: According to your country, 7-60 days. If it has not been received for more than 60 days, we will refund you.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">3) Q: What should I do if there is a quality issue with the product?</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">A: Contact us and we will solve the problem.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">If the buyer wants to know more about the shipping cost, please contact us and we will provide a reasonable shipping option.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">\u2728shipment</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">1) Consignment</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">We support drop shipping and can send your order to your customers. Please leave your licensed address when you place your order.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">2) Delivery time</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">AliExpress standard transportation: 15-60 days</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">Please note that due to customer and weather reasons, there may be some delays, but we will extend the delivery time for you, so please be patient and wait for a period of time.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">\u2728payment</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">1) We accept third-party hosting, Boleto, Visa, MasterCard, QIWI, Western Union remittance, Maestro debit card, WebMoney, bank transfer, credit card, and any payment method that can be made on Global AliExpress.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">2) Custody is the safest payment method.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">\u2728Guarantee and Guarantee</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">1) If there is quality damage to the goods, we will provide a 12 month warranty period and purchase with confidence</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">2) All products are brand new and have passed quality inspection.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">3) If you are not satisfied after receiving it and want to return it, please return or refund within 3 days.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">Please contact us before returning the item. But the item must be in the original state we sent you</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">4) We accept good suggestions from buyers and strive to provide a better shopping experience.</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">We constantly provide discounts for buyers!</p></div><div class=\"detailmodule_text\"><div><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></div><p style=\"font-family:OpenSans;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:20px;white-space:pre-wrap;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin-bottom:12px\" class=\"detail-desc-decorate-content\">\u2728If you have any questions, please contact us and we will reply to you within 24 hours. If you are satisfied with our service, please give us a five-star review. Thank you and wish you a pleasant day!</p></div><div><br/></div></div></div><p><br/></p>"
